      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single load level (ASTM F1717 standard protocol, ambient conditions). Environmental conditions documented and within ASTM-specified tolerances. However, only a single test condition (compression-bending at standard offset) was evaluated; no variation in load magnitude or offset distance. This limits the achieved gradation to 2, below the required gradation 3. Risk accepted given that the COU is also restricted to standard F1717 conditions.",
