    "rationale": "All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified quantitative acceptance criterion (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%). Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved gradation 2 vs. required 3) is accepted because the COU is explicitly restricted to the standard ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration, and no extrapolation beyond this condition is intended. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level conclusion for this Class II device submission.",
